{
  "screen_id": "qr-resume",
  "route": "/qr/resume",
  "title": "観測を再開する",
  "layout": "standard",
  "notes": "wave1-obs R1(QR→観測の最短導線): /qr/{token} の3解決(個体QR/棚QR占有/棚QR空)を画面側で分岐(observation-routes.ts GET /qr/:token)。空の棚(entry_mode=qr_placement_empty・individual_id:null)は『個体が見つかりました』と偽らず新規個体登録へ導く(旧: resumeボタンがid=nullで追観測へ死路になっていた・OBS目的宣言『最少クリックで記録』の綻び)。分岐はrenderer props.when(eq/not_eq・NodeView先頭で全ノード評価)のみで表現し、schemas/・renderer.tsx・共有物は無改変。占有パスの文言(個体が見つかりました/個体 ID:/この個体で観測を続ける)は既存E2E(observation.spec §7-8)の資産のため不変で維持。wave1-obs R2(persona R75・棚は複数個体を同時に保持できる): projectOccupantAt が最初の1件だけ返し多頭棚を無言で1個体に潰していた欠陥を是正(source-routes.ts projectOccupantsAt)。entry_mode=qr_placement_multi(2+在棚)は新規分岐で個体を選ばせる(GET /individuals一覧と同じ行データ=individual-routes.ts summarizeIndividualRow/projectIndividualSummary を再利用・二重実装しない)。R3でQRスキャン→紐付け側を追加予定。wave1-obs R4(OBS-R4・個体を特定した後の紐づけハブ): 占有(個体特定)パスに『この個体に紐づける』3導線を純加算 — ①追観測=既存 resume ボタン(この個体で観測を続ける→obs-register-entry・E2E資産のため文言不変)②棚=obs-register-batch へのリンク(既存 move/occupancy 導線)③繁殖=obs-register-clutch?parent_id=<individual_id> へ navigate し、スキャンした個体を親候補として自動セット(ClutchIntakeNode が params.parent_id を先読み)。ハブは全て when(not_eq individual_id \"\")で占有パス限定・navigation.json 無改変(既存 batch リンクと同じ node 表現)。所有権整合(R4新設ガード): 追観測=POST /observation/captures と /solid-observation/commit・繁殖=POST /clutches の親個体所有権を projectCurrentOwner で fail-closed 403 NOT_OWNER 化(他人の個体は特定/閲覧のみ・記録追加不可=承認予想図の正直split どおり)。schemas/renderer.tsx グローバルナビは無改変。",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "shell",
      "type": "app-shell",
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "page",
          "type": "page",
          "children": [
            {
              "id": "title-page",
              "type": "heading",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.page-title.text",
                "text": "観測を再開する",
                "level": 1
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "title-found",
              "type": "heading",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.title.text",
                "text": "個体が見つかりました",
                "level": 2,
                "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "title-empty",
              "type": "heading",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.title-empty.text",
                "text": "空の棚です",
                "level": 2,
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_empty"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "title-multi",
              "type": "heading",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.title-multi.text",
                "text": "この棚の個体を選ぶ",
                "level": 2,
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_multi"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "lead-found",
              "type": "text",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.lead.text",
                "text": "この個体の文脈で、前回値を引き継いで観測を続けます。",
                "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "lead-empty",
              "type": "text",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.lead-empty.text",
                "text": "この棚にはまだ個体がいません。この棚で新規個体を登録できます。",
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_empty"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "lead-multi",
              "type": "text",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.lead-multi.text",
                "text": "この棚には複数の個体がいます。観測する個体を選んでください。",
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_multi"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "resolve",
              "type": "card",
              "props": { "source_path": "/api/v1/qr/{{params.token}}?prefill=1" },
              "children": [
                {
                  "id": "ind-id",
                  "type": "text",
                  "props": {
                    "text_key": "qr-resume.ind-id.text",
                    "text": "個体 ID: {{data.resolve.individual_id}}",
                    "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "prefill-species",
                  "type": "text",
                  "props": {
                    "text_key": "qr-resume.prefill-species.text",
                    "text": "前回の種の候補: {{data.resolve.prefill.species_candidate}}",
                    "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "placement-id",
                  "type": "text",
                  "props": {
                    "text_key": "qr-resume.placement-id.text",
                    "text": "棚 ID: {{data.resolve.placement_id}}",
                    "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_empty"] }
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "occupants-table",
              "type": "table",
              "props": {
                "bind_items": "data.resolve.occupants",
                "empty_text": "在棚の個体が取得できませんでした。",
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_multi"] },
                "columns": [
                  { "key": "label", "label": "個体" },
                  { "key": "species", "label": "種" },
                  {
                    "key": "last_capture_at",
                    "label": "最終観測",
                    "cell": "observed",
                    "measurement_key": "last_measurement_summary"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "individual_id",
                    "label": "",
                    "cell": "link",
                    "href_tpl": "/s/obs-register-entry?id={{individual_id}}",
                    "link_label": "追観測へ →"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "add-to-shelf",
              "type": "link",
              "props": {
                "label_key": "qr-resume.add-to-shelf.label",
                "label": "この棚に新規個体を追加 →",
                "href": "/s/obs-register-new",
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_multi"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "link-to-batch-multi",
              "type": "link",
              "props": {
                "label_key": "qr-resume.link-to-batch.label",
                "label": "この棚に個体を移して紐づける →",
                "href": "/s/obs-register-batch",
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_multi"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "link-to-batch-empty",
              "type": "link",
              "props": {
                "label_key": "qr-resume.link-to-batch.label",
                "label": "この棚に個体を移して紐づける →",
                "href": "/s/obs-register-batch",
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_empty"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "hub-title",
              "type": "heading",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.hub-title.text",
                "text": "この個体に紐づける",
                "level": 3,
                "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "resume",
              "type": "button",
              "props": {
                "label_key": "qr-resume.resume.label",
                "label": "この個体で観測を続ける",
                "variant": "primary",
                "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
              },
              "action": { "kind": "navigate", "to": "obs-register-entry?id={{data.resolve.individual_id}}" }
            },
            {
              "id": "hub-shelf",
              "type": "link",
              "props": {
                "label_key": "qr-resume.hub-shelf.label",
                "label": "棚に置く・移す →",
                "href": "/s/obs-register-batch",
                "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "hub-clutch",
              "type": "button",
              "props": {
                "label_key": "qr-resume.hub-clutch.label",
                "label": "繁殖(クラッチ)に親として記録 →",
                "variant": "secondary",
                "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
              },
              "action": { "kind": "navigate", "to": "obs-register-clutch?parent_id={{data.resolve.individual_id}}" }
            },
            {
              "id": "resume-new",
              "type": "button",
              "props": {
                "label_key": "qr-resume.resume-new.label",
                "label": "この棚で新規個体を登録",
                "variant": "primary",
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_empty"] }
              },
              "action": { "kind": "navigate", "to": "obs-register-new" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "transitions": [
    { "from": "resume", "to_screen_id": "obs-register-entry", "label": "個体文脈付きで観測入力へ(OBS-25正本フロー)" },
    { "from": "resume-new", "to_screen_id": "obs-register-new", "label": "空の棚から新規個体登録へ" }
  ]
}
